creator: Marco Olvera
descriptionHtml:
With PixelYear you can keep track of all your moods during the year, with personalized colors, as well as being able to visualize them in a grid representing the whole year in pixels.
Each pixel corresponds to one day of the year.
You can add unlimited moods or emotions; Although it is not limited to only moods, you can also keep track of your productivity for example.

It serves as an intimate diary since you can add notes for each day to record your activities.

Customize your moods and emotions.

Set your daily reminder so you do not forget a single day.

You can also share the results with your friends.

PixelYear does not store your personal data, they are under your control.
descriptionShort: Keep a record of your days and visualize your year in pixels.

title: PixelYear: Year in Pixels

creator: Marco Olvera
descriptionHtml:
Now with backup system!

With PixelYear you can keep a journal or keep track of all your moods during the year, with customizable colors, as well as being able to visualize them in a grid representing the whole year in pixels.
Each pixel corresponds to a day of the year.
You can add unlimited moods or emotions; Although it is not limited to only moods, you can also keep track of your productivity for example.

Customize your moods and emotions.

Set your daily reminder so you do not forget a single day.

You can also share the results with your friends.

PixelYear can store your data to your Google Drive, this data is under your control protected with your Google credentials.
